OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fdry with some low cloud and fog in the
OL,9,Feast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FDry and sunny but cloud may
OL,12,Flinger along some North Sea coastal
OL,13,Fdistricts. Warm inland, but very warm
OL,14,For hot in the southwest. Eastern
OL,15,Fcoastal areas cooler.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,18,Fdry few days with good spells of
OL,19,Fsunshine. Warm in the west with the
OL,20,Fbest of the sunshine, cloudier and
OL,21,Fcooler at times in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
